  <summary date="2025-04-25T01:51:43Z" status="Introduced in House">Lower Grocery Prices Act

This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to submit a report to Congress on changes in the Consumer Price Index for food at home over the past 20 years. The report must also include recommendations to help lower food at home costs for U.S. consumers.</summary>
